question: Hi, my name Anna. I'm going to ask you a few questions. You can skip anything you want to. Are you ready to get started?
What is your most urgent need?
When was the last time you ate?
Where are you located?
How old are you?
What is your race or ethnicity?
What gender do you identify as?
Do you identify as trans?
What is your sexual orientation?
Are you married or have you ever been married?
What is the highest level of education you have?
Do you have any trade skills or licenses?
Are you employed? If so, how many hours a week do you work?
What is your approximate monthly income?
Do you have reliable personal transportation, or do you have access to someone else's transportation??
What is your current housing situation? Are you currently renting, staying with a friend, living in your car, living on the street or other?
How many people live with you? Do you have any dependents? (children, elders, pets, roomates)
Do you have a mailing address? If so, what is it?
Are there any other adults who live at that address?
Are you a military veteran? If so, which branch?
Have you ever worked for the federal, state, or local government? If so, which department?
If you have been convicted of a felony, would you be interested in participating in a program to help felons re-entering the workforce?
Have you been the victim of domestic or sexual violence, assault, or abuse?
Do you have any outstanding debts, including things like student loans or credit card debts? Approximately how much do you owe?
Are you on or have you used government services before?
Have worked with a non-profit group for assistance?
Thanks, that's all the questions I have right now. I really appreciate your help! May I have your email address so I can send you a follow up email?
